nd simplify rendering code by adopting newer APIs.\r\n\r\n### Dependency Updates:\r\n* Updated Bevy dependencies and related libraries to newer versions (`Cargo.toml`). This includes moving from `0.12.0` to `0.16.1` for Bevy and adding `bevy-inspector-egui` for debugging and visualization purposes.\r\n\r\n### Rendering and Color Handling:\r\n* Replaced `bevy_render::Color` with `bevy_color::Color` and updated color definitions to use sRGB for more accurate color representation across multiple files (`src/sparse_voxel_octree.rs`, `src/voxelized_mesh.rs`). [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-1f4042c89efa76afddca8c421ec60d18459ef43639afc1611a254026fece6926L349-R349) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-1f4042c89efa76afddca8c421ec60d18459ef43639afc1611a254026fece6926L524-R524) [[3]](diffhunk://#diff-1f4042c89efa76afddca8c421ec60d18459ef43639afc1611a254026fece6926L554-R560) [[4]](diffhunk://#diff-0896fc7a075d7991456bca839519f0d6fec4d0419f3fd4cb7285c7ab9157bda5L187-R186)\r\n\r\n### Examples Refactoring:\r\n* Refactored examples (`examples/bevy_sphere.rs` and `examples/bevy_sphere_path.rs`) to use updated APIs, including replacing `UVSphere` with `Sphere`, simplifying camera setup, and adding `WorldInspectorPlugin` for debugging. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-0aaaab87c6a0b7d8ebdff1cd4c7a66372d04b3606380cd8651b86d9880b51682L2-R10) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-0aaaab87c6a0b7d8ebdff1cd4c7a66372d04b3606380cd8651b86d9880b51682L26-R33) [[3]](diffhunk://#diff-0aaaab87c6a0b7d8ebdff1cd4c7a66372d04b3606380cd8651b86d9880b51682L43-R62) [[4]](diffhunk://#diff-0f34e77ba911e10bc7189c9a977e7e572f72a69e8d5558f49cd89a1f8211a490L2-R10) [[5]](diffhunk://#diff-0f34e77ba911e10bc7189c9a977e7e572f72a69e8d5558f49cd89a1f8211a490L47-R56) [[6]](diffhunk://#diff-0f34e77ba911e10bc7189c9a977e7e572f72a69e8d5558f49cd89a1f8211a490L75-R101)\r\n\r\n### Benchmark Fixes:\r\n* Removed redundant `black_box` import from `criterion` in `benches/pathing_around_sphere.rs`.\r\n\r\n### Minor Improvements:\r\n* Replaced deprecated method calls (`delta_seconds` â†’ `delta_secs`) and improved query handling in `examples/bevy_sphere_path.rs`. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-0f34e77ba911e10bc7189c9a977e7e572f72a69e8d5558f49cd89a1f8211a490L248-R252) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-0f34e77ba911e10bc7189c9a977e7e572f72a69e8d5558f49cd89a1f8211a490L271-R275)\r\n\r\n## Demo\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2da3da49-3621-482f-9bf5-e24b8a8f6a58)\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mkmarek/svo-rs/issues/1/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mkmarek/svo-rs/issues/1/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"}]